dct_title_s: Mapa de la Ciudad de Mendoza : calles - alturas avenidas - plazas, edificios públicos, referencias turísticas, accesos - autopistas / cartografia Guillermo Cimarelli.
dct_description_sm: Shows roads, traffic flow circulation shown by red arrows, public buildings , places of worship, cemeteries, and tourists sites. Bottom of cover panel: Latinbaires Editores S.R.L. Top of cover panel: 40. Ancillary map: "Accesos de la Ciudad de Mendoza". Ancillary map: "San Martin" Includes: index to streets, and location maps.
